des: "A sauce/spread for a Bosnian sandwich using lepinja bread and cevapcici sausage that I saw on diners/drive-ins and dives and didn't see a recipe for this on this site so here's one!"
ins: Press feta cheese through a sieve until most of liquid has drained. Beat drained feta cheese, sour cream, and cream cheese in a bowl until smooth. Refrigerate until flavors blend, at least 30 minutes. Bring to room temperature before serving.
